# Pull Request Checklist

Thank you for contributing to **AREG-SDK**! Please confirm the following before submitting:

- [ ] I have read and understood the **[AREG-SDK Contributor License Agreement (CLA) v1.0](../CONTRIBUTOR_LICENSE_AGREEMENT.md)**.
- [ ] By submitting this pull request, I **agree to the CLA**, granting the Project an irrevocable license to use my contribution under Apache 2.0 and/or a commercial license.
- [ ] I confirm that the contribution is my original work or I have the right to submit it.
- [ ] I have included a copyright notice in my files if I want to retain copyright.

**Note:** By checking these boxes and submitting, you automatically agree to the CLA.
